'''Grant Murphy''' is an administrator at the facility where [[Georgie Schwartz]] lived.

==History==
Grant called in Sam and Amelia, knowing their practice had done good things. He needed them to talk to [[Bob Schwartz]] about his wife, [[Georgie Schwartz]], who was comatose after a skiing accident.

When their tests discovered that Georgie was pregnant, Grant asked them for time to figure it out before they called the police, believing someone who worked at the facility had raped her. It later came out that Bob was the one who had raped her.

==Career==
He is an administrator at a long-term care facility.
